em of what to with your time\n\n- Sunday\n|\nI think Lafayette wants to rap in French now. I have to go learn some French.Damn it, Lafayette\n\n- Lin Manuel Miranda, Hamillton\n|\nAnd the thing is, we can’t fail. We’ve already hit the bottom and come out of it. From here on out, if we just love and listen, we can’t go wrong, babe.\n\n- Erin McCarthy, Hot Finish\n|\nRemember, Hope is a good thing, maybe the best of things, and no good thing ever dies.\n\n- Stephen\n|\nThe greatest violence, and the greatest threat to humanity, is the growth of MONEY.\n\n- Compton\n|\nPeople say that a dog can sense the longing of a person, so perhaps he's barking in response to your heart.\n\n- Kim Dong Hwa, The Color of Water\n|\nUnasked, Unsought, Love gives itself but is not bought\n\n- Henry Wadsworth Longfellow, The Complete Works of Henry Wadsworth Longfellow\n|\n‎‎‎‎‎‎‎‎‎‎‎‎‎‎‎‎‎‎‎The mind of God is greater than all the minds of men, so let all men leave the gospel just as God has delivered it unto us.\n\n- Charles Haddon Spurgeon, Spurgeon's Sermons Vol. 1-10\n|\nThrough challenge and difficulty, we learn to see life differently than before.\n\n- Auliq-Ice\n|\nIt didn’t look like a solid hand; it looked like paper, almost transparent in the light. Just as suddenly the hand was pulled back and the window went black.\n\n- Sian\n|\nNot all people are 'people', some are more and some are less. But only those who listen intently with their hearts will recognise them for what they are.\n\n- Wayne\n|\nYour absence has not taught me to be alone, it merely has shown that when together we cast a single shadow on the wall.\n\n- Doug\n|\nSuccess means having the courage, the determination, and the will to become the person you believe you were meant to be.\n\n- George\n|\nThey say that not matter how old you become, when you are with your siblings, you revert back to childhood.\n\n- Karen   White, The Memory of Water\n|\nI hate the day, because it lendeth lightTo see all things, but not 